***** ASSUMABLE RATE MORTGAGE AT 3.071% AVAILABLE FOR VA BUYERS ***** 
*** SELLER CONCESSION FOR CARPET ALLOWANCE ***
Welcome to your new home in Crystal Valley Ranch! 5 Bedroom / 4 Full Baths / 3 Car Garage. This Castle Rock location is minutes away from Downtown where you can enjoy the fun-filled Vibe of Restaurants, Shops, Coffee shops, Breweries, Outdoor concerts and more! Near Rhyolite Park, Phillip Miller Park, and endless Trail systems. The community includes a clubhouse, fitness center, pool, and Douglas County Schools. The Floorplan features an open concept main floor living space with high-quality Vinyl plank Flooring, Quartz countertops, Stainless Steel Appliances, a walk in pantry, a large island with barstools, office, bedroom with walk in closet, and a full bath. Upstairs features a Primary Bedroom with attached Retreat, a Large closet with a second closet in the ensuite bath! Upstairs Laundry! The Vinyl plank flooring extends into the Primary Bedroom and Upstairs Hallways for low maintenance. Upstairs also includes, Bedroom 1 with an ensuite bathroom and a walk in closet, a loft, Bedrooms 2 & 3, and Bathroom with double sinks. There is Room to grow in the unfinished basement that is plumbed for a bath.
